        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31422481/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31422481/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/waiterli/" class=" " title="倚天">倚天</a>
                (大成若缺)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31422481">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">今个儿，翻阅该书，忽然感觉，朱总理的讲话平实，信息量很大，不像我们的通常的领导讲话，排比连篇，句式工整，却无味道。还是平实为贵。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-04-29 17:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
